** element -> caller -> handler **

- when create element
 - set element -> caller
 - set caller -> onLoad
- when element added,
  - call onLoad
  - set target element -> source element caller
- when element morphed,
  - if target element caller !== source element caller
    - call source element onLoad
    - call target element onUnload
    - set target element -> source element caller
- when element removed,
  - call onUnload
  - remove target element caller
